{"type":null,"faqId":26420,"title":"Recovering the microSD Card","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei','sans-serif';\ncolor:#9900CC;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150601211845818001.png\" style=\"width:375pt;height:187.5pt\"></span></b></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">Recovering\nthe microSD Card</span></b></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif'\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';text-indent:21.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\ncolor:#7030A0\">Has your phone ever displayed a message saying \"The microSD\ncard is damaged, please reformat it\"? This document helps you recover the\nmicroSD card without reformatting it. </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"font-family:'Microsoft YaHei','sans-serif';\ncolor:#7030A0;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150601211846807002.png\" style=\"width:238.5pt;height:146.25pt\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif'\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\ncolor:#7030A0;\">1. Connect your phone to a computer. On the\ncomputer, find the movable disk corresponding to the microSD card in <b>My Computer</b>. </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\ncolor:#7030A0;\">2. Click <b>Start</b> &gt; <b>Run</b>.</span><span style=\"font-family:'Microsoft YaHei','sans-serif';\ncolor:#7030A0;\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\ncolor:#7030A0;\">3. Run <b>chkdsk\n/f </b><i>Drive Letter</i>. The variable is\nthe drive letter of the microSD card. </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\ncolor:#7030A0;\">4. Press <b>Enter</b>. </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\ncolor:#7030A0;\">5. Right-click the microSD card's drive\nletter, click <b>Properties</b> &gt; <b>Tools</b> &gt; <b>Check now</b>, and select <b>Automatically\nfix file system errors</b> and <b>Scan for\nand attempt recovery of bad sectors</b>. </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\ncolor:#7030A0;\">(Make sure you select these two options.\nOtherwise the recovery may fail.)</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"font-family:'Microsoft YaHei','sans-serif';\ncolor:#7030A0;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150601211852431003.png\" style=\"width:415.5pt;height:249.75pt\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif'\">&nbsp;</p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":1,"languageName":"en","faqCode":"799","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1433164743000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":2,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"Recovering the microSD Card","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}